  "texts": [
    "Amy launches DesignPrompt, and an interface containing a search engine, moodboard canvas, image meta-data display and AI image generation tool shows up as shown in Fig. 2.",
    "She starts by searching keywords such as \"living room\", \"cozy sofa\" and \"plant\" at the search engine panel on the left (1), and scrolls to view more results.",
    "She drags and drops the images onto the canvas (Fig. 2.a) and then resizes and rotates some images on canvas by double-clicking them.",
    "As Amy drags more images onto the canvas, the color palette at the bottom left of the canvas starts to build up.",
    "She single clicks on the sofa image and additional semantic and color information are displayed on the bottom (Fig. 2.b), which she explores for new search ideas.Amy then decides to generate images to refine her ideas."
